         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition note</head>
         <p>Ongoing collection of documents acquired by gift and purchase from various sources. Type of accesion (gift or purchase) and date of acquisition is noted in the box-and-folder listing. For further information, consult the appropriate curator.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
